{"tid":1566122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<一人寄十封信返大陸>","createTime":"2019-09-13T12:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:18:37.000Z","uid":268541,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"528c49875340700ba733276b7deec221b43e598d","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:15:51.000Z","msg":"利申：我個有睇連登的阿叔 叫我幫佢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足, 我有一個建議想攞出來畀大家討論, 有點長, 但希望大家認真研究<br />\n<br />\n今時今日, 呢場運動林奠已經無話事權, 而中共宜家的態度係想拖, 一來唔想做決定, 二來想拖死場運動, 我覺得可以做啲野迫佢<br />\n<br />\n大家向海外做大量文宣, 都係想外國向中共施加壓力, 但大家有無諗過, 相對於外國的影響, 中共其實更忌內部威脅, 如果唔係中共唔使每年用唔多錢維穩, 同埋大家應該仲記得, 呢場運動開始無耐, 曾經爆出[福獨]/[廣獨]的風, 令大陸擔心在內地發酵, 因而要轉低調處理, 我覺得可以嘗試製造呢種內部威脅, 或者製造一個現象, 令對方覺得有內部威脅<br />\n<br />\n要透過互聯網去製造呢種威脅, 現實上不太可能, 就算做都好大風險, 因為大陸的網絡監控已經係世界級, 我大膽提出用一個古老方法：寄信<br />\n<br />\n我哋寄信返大陸, 信入面有呢場運動的信息, 作用有兩個, 一, 如果封信真係寄得到畀收信人, 就當向大陸人做文宣, 希望有人接收到呢方面的信息, 二, 即使封信畀公安等系統截住, 就讓他們知道, 香港人正嘗試用呢種方法, 令運動在內地發酵<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法好處係便宜, 每封信都係幾蚊雞, 十封都唔使一嚿水, 如果有公司, 平時有大量信件要寄番大陸, 印多兩個信封, 攝幾封落去都唔多覺, 而不論寄唔寄到畀目標人物, 都達到其中一個目標<br />\n<br />\n透過呢種方法, 可以預期其實好大比率的信, 有機會畀保安系統的人截左, 但唔緊要, 我哋係要製造一個現象, 令中共覺得, 我哋嘗試攻入大陸, 佢哋唔會想件事响大陸發酵, 就會想快啲解決<br />\n<br />\n執行方法：<br />\n<br />\n內容：如果有人可以幫設計多個範本, 兩張紙的內容, 用殘體字及內地用語, 簡介呢場運動, 講番香港警察已經公安化, 運動唔係要搞港獨, 係追求民主, 同埋請求收信人, 將信息傳開去<br />\n <br />\n寄信對象：任何人, 當然唔好寄畀自己親戚朋友(除非你同佢有仇), 只要上網按大家喜好,搵唔同的大陸人, 可以是任何機構, 有名有姓有真實地址, 如果有何妖之類人物, 响大陸親友地址, 都不妨寄出, 領導人親友就更佳啦, 如果可以做到, 各省各縣各市, 都有人收到信, 可以更加令中共感到威脅<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n準備信件過程, 最好戴手套, 或者手指塗膠水, 避免留下指紋<br />\n千祈唔好用口水貼郵票同信封, 避免留下DNA<br />\n唔使留回郵地址, 要留可以留民賤聯等中資機構<br />\n寄件時使用郵筒好過去郵局<br />\n信封最好扮工務信件, 送得到目的地的機會會大一點<br />\n<br />\n如果可以擴大到, 各球都有人寄呢封信, 要截查的難度就更加大, 同埋如果有內地人, 如果有朋友可以响內地寄, 可以加深中共害怕運動發酵的恐懼, 當然這個風險很高, 要真係確保安全先好做<br />\n<br />\n如果大家認同做法可行, 就幫手推啦, 謝謝"},{"pid":"74bd4310b598b3c8b25ad861c64f4fee75dfaef5","tid":1566122,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23ab4cd84ed3f416d49c4350da7a4682b3479880","tid":1566122,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64c610bbcc6f618b292356bd74b4bfeac782f61a","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月15 12點英領 3點銅鑼灣</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0caa607a43aea4d1566be26784ee95aed1a22795","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:17:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月15 12點英領 3點銅鑼灣</span></strong>"},{"pid":"85d8a4a4871f9d3c7eea81364b102d45939358db","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月15 12點英領 3點銅鑼灣</span></strong>"},{"pid":"78ad7c34f7b9b7671204da32c3279875c6212143","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月15 12點英領 3點銅鑼灣</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e8f1ce4a23f2280875d3c07f04572c2185827b82","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"大家覺得有用or有意見就留下言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個阿叔係到mon緊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc135d7f4c32534dc4c724e2a34ae50bb776d59","tid":1566122,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"要搵地址, 可能要埋收件人"},{"pid":"f03557e962cb8afbe3980d1e40635b8ded1f7621","tid":1566122,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"可以不只寄信 <br />\n寄usb隨身碟 <br />\n裡面有64 /反送中 /雨傘/中國各地抗爭的影片 <br />\n和所有共產黨的惡行惡狀<br />\n各種被禁的書的電子檔<br />\n各種文宣 理念宣傳<br />\n<br />\n或者做一個範本檔 時時更新 <br />\n想寄的人 就上網抓最新版的寄 <br />\n反正一個2gb的就可以裝超多東西了 <br />\n也沒多少錢"},{"pid":"2ede9ef1aa7d615c3ea10e7e9a2efd00568eb8c6","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03557e962cb8afbe3980d1e40635b8ded1f7621","tid":1566122,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"可以不只寄信 <br />\n寄usb隨身碟 <br />\n裡面有64 /反送中 /雨傘/中國各地抗爭的影片 <br />\n和所有共產黨的惡行惡狀<br />\n各種被禁的書的電子檔<br />\n各種文宣 理念宣傳<br />\n<br />\n或者做一個範本檔 時時更新 <br />\n想寄的人 就上網抓最新版的寄 <br />\n反正一個2gb的就可以裝超多東西了 <br />\n也沒多少錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"之前有post提過派usb比遊客<br />\n最後好似不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488dcb957ac48f34670ae5bb080ac3224e248b2b","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"915 港島見"},{"pid":"6b80b3c31a8b8284997dfccfade6e0b680f4ebc5","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"915 港島見"},{"pid":"ed4f5fc950574e6c5da2ffc415c2667ef85fb27b","tid":1566122,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ede9ef1aa7d615c3ea10e7e9a2efd00568eb8c6","tid":1566122,"uid":268541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03557e962cb8afbe3980d1e40635b8ded1f7621","tid":1566122,"uid":295039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"可以不只寄信 <br />\n寄usb隨身碟 <br />\n裡面有64 /反送中 /雨傘/中國各地抗爭的影片 <br />\n和所有共產黨的惡行惡狀<br />\n各種被禁的書的電子檔<br />\n各種文宣 理念宣傳<br />\n<br />\n或者做一個範本檔 時時更新 <br />\n想寄的人 就上網抓最新版的寄 <br />\n反正一個2gb的就可以裝超多東西了 <br />\n也沒多少錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"之前有post提過派usb比遊客<br />\n最後好似不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"派USB給遊客 &nbsp;遊客應該不敢帶著過海關吧 會直接丟掉<br />\n如果可以直接寄到中國 &nbsp;<br />\n100個中就算只有一個被打開來看 並且傳給其他人 就值得了 <br />\nUSB 上最好還標註一些可能會讓人好奇的文字<br />\n讓人一定想開來看一下<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕三件事<br />\n1.在港經濟利益受影響 &lt;--已經在做了<br />\n2.外國制裁 &lt;-已經在做了<br />\n3.民主浪潮蔓延中國 &lt;- 好像沒做很多<br />\n<br />\n3雖然效果很慢 但只有3 最後才能讓中國共產黨垮台<br />\n根本的解決所有問題<br />\n<br />\n要做中共最怕的事才有效果<br />\n而且不管在哪個國家都可以寄 <br />\nUSB 又小 <br />\n中國無法全擋下來 <br />\n感覺不錯 <br />\n<br />\nStep 1<br />\n建立一個網站 蒐集所有中國害怕曝光的資料<br />\n提供下載 時時更新<br />\n例: 64/反送中/各種民主思潮禁書電子書 <br />\n<br />\nStep 2.<br />\n人人下載存到USB 寄出 (剛查了一下 16G 的才25 &nbsp;HKD 不到)<br />\n<br />\n收件對象 北上廣深各大城市的民眾/五毛/公司行號<br />\n大城市的民眾比較有見過世面 比較有獨立思考的能力"},{"pid":"e7374a433c140984c0e12c94d4ac58105d213ab1","tid":1566122,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"671b8be4f4fa2e8fbb9b3d805c9a24ebb6d23e8d","tid":1566122,"uid":315752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"郵局同大陸果邊實晨早驗屍咁驗<br />\n仲要而家十一前夕、禁酒令都出哂黎<br />\n<br />\n倒不如你狂寄野俾我地啲狗仔同佢狗仔女屋企先<br />\n扮送禮、宣傳咩都得<br />\n最多都係份禮太大嚇親下"}]}